01:08:31.240 --> 01:08:39.820
<v John>Like, it's, so it doesn't matter whether you can, and in fact, you can only have, you would say, you can only have ontological and theological reappropriations, right?</v>

01:08:40.300 --> 01:08:56.040
<v Nate>Well, that's such a key, that's such a key part of this definition of difference that I feel like is often lost in its appropriation or interpretation, where it's like that dual, it's not only the condition of possibility for life in general.</v>

